snippet.title: Rising Up (trailer) - Climb the Corporate Ladder... with Your Fists!
snippet.description:
Unleash office mayhem! Leaving a trail of paperwork, shattered furniture, and fallen co-workers as you battle your way to the top!
Free to play at: https://twitwi.itch.io/risingup
Listen to the soundtrack here: https://album.link/anoint

Credits:
Art by LAURENT GEHIN
Programming by EVALINE HØYRUP JØRGENSEN
Music by ANOINT BAND
Sound by NIKOLAJ DE HAAN
